			<div class="self-center grid gap-6">
				<div class="grid gap-2">
					<h1 class="self-center text-4xl font-semibold">Medieval Reception of the Roman Conquest of Jerusalem </h1>
					<h2 class="self-center text-2xl italic">The Roman conquest of Jerusalem in 70 AD: Reception, use, and interpretation in the Middle Ages (c.600-c.1200)</h2>
				</div>
